rating_comment: It was an wonderful stay, with all amenities and lovely host.will visit again
The place was Cozy and Peaceful, felt right at home and it was easy to find the place

Affordable and comfortable stay in an apartment. The host Abhinand was very responsive and helpful. Also has a full time security guard who is also very helpful
But there is no lift and the road to reach the apartment is bad.
It was a really nice stay. Spacious rooms, clean toilets and a kitted kitchen with a working fridge. Felt at home here.
It was a great experience staying at Abhinand's place. He was very responsive and there was everything you need we even cooked our own food. Had an amazing time there.
The cozy space, thoughtful amenities and host's friendliness and attention to every small problem made it feel like a home far away from home.

Nice and comfortable stay for family. It is slightly far from NJP station but to catch early morning train, I was able to reach NJP in 15 mins. Rooms were clean and comfortable. Nice place if you want to stay overnight.
The stay was very comfortable. Abhinand is a great host and made the early check in process very smooth for us. Highly recommend :)
Had a great time at Abhinand's place. He was really helpful and good natured.Staybwas amazing and comfortable.
Great host and excellent location.
Absolutely perfect for staycation...nice value.... Really worth it... 10/10
very helpful host... I would highly recommend this place... a very peaceful place...

First of all, if you're traveling with foreigners, especially women, it's really nice to stay, and it's a place in the form of an apartment, and there's a security guard, so I'm so relieved.
And the house was really spacious, and there was air conditioning in each room, so I think I had a very pleasant life at home.
I don't know how nice it was because the host responded really quickly if we needed anything or needed help. 🥹 We were able to adapt quickly here. The washing machine and refrigerator tableware were all good, and the bathroom was clean.
If I come back to Siliguri again, I think I want to stay here a lot.
However, sometimes bugs come out, but you can solve that with bug medicine.. I don't think you have to panic too much:) Thank you for providing such a nice house

A very tidy and lovely Airbnb apartment equipped with everything you need. Abhinand is a great host and there when you need him. He was also very helpful since the beginning, available at all times whenever I had any questions. Very nice and communication was super easy and quick.The place looks exactly like it does in the pictures. We had a great stay.. Would absolutely recommend staying there!
It’s a delight to stay at this place, everything well went! Abhinand you have my highest recommendation!
Easy and convenient, good for the price paid
The stay was good. Abinand was quite helpful and we had a comfortable stay during the vacation.
A great stay at this price & all rooms had air conditioner installed.

abhinandan is a good guy he will do everything to make ur stay pleasant and place is also neat and clean veryapproachable for those who travel with their own car as it has a dedicated car parking.
he owns a place at Darjeeling too so after siliguri u can go to his place at darjeling.
Good place to stay. Abhinandan has been a great host.
Hi Abhinand, thanks a lot. It was a comfortable stay at your house. We felt totally homely environment there. Thanks a lot again.
What stood out was the host, Abhinand. He was just so friendly, helpful and so dedicated to helping my family when they had a problem. Thank you so much, Abihinand.
